AUTO_CREATE_USER_AUTHENTICATION

public static final RuleRegistry.Callout AUTO_CREATE_USER_AUTHENTICATION
Join point called when pass-through authentication is successful but the account does not correlate to a user, which results in a new user being created. This rule transforms the user.

IDENTITY_CORRELATION

public static final RuleRegistry.Callout IDENTITY_CORRELATION
Default rule used to correlate an application account to an existing Identity after pass-through authentication or during aggregation.

IDENTITY_REFRESH

public static final RuleRegistry.Callout IDENTITY_REFRESH
Default rule run on each identity cube during a refresh. This is the last step in the refresh process.
